title: 205: Monday Night Football Recap, FSU HC Jimbo Fisher
itunes:title: 205: Monday Night Football Recap, FSU HC Jimbo Fisher
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks recap all of the action from both Week 1 “Monday Night Football” games. The guys also review the huge weekend that was in college football before bringing on Florida State head coach Jimbo Fisher to profile his blue-chip safety, Derwin James.
